{
  "text": "I have guessed that a way that I could enter into a better comprehension of the development and experience that is central to our work is to compare what we experience now after the veil is drawn with what was experienced prior to that time, starting possibly as far back as the beginning of this octave of experience, to see how we got into the condition we're in now. If this is agreeable, I would like to retreat to the very beginning of this octave of experience to investigate the conditions mind, body, and spirit as they evolved in this octave. Is this satisfactory or acceptable? I am well the direction of a question is your approval.",
